request.doc:
Creating a user with group memberships:
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/sysaccount/users/v1
POST_DATA: 
{
    "id":"testuser",
    "password": "Passw0rd",
    "groups": [
        {"id":"testgroup"}
    ]
}


Creating a user without any group membership:
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/sysaccount/users/v1
POST_DATA: 
{
    "id":"testuser",
    "password": "Passw0rd"
}
